4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive AI Machine Learning Engineer course designed for beginners, requiring no prior knowledge. Over 16 weeks, students can expect 3 classes per week in small groups. The curriculum covers Python, SQL, and various analytical tools, enabling participants to build and deploy predictive models using supervised and unsupervised learning techniques.

The course is led by experienced instructors, including a PhD in AI from Toronto University and a Machine Learning Scientist from ISTAT. Graduates receive a recognized certificate and can choose instruction in either English or Spanish. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop